{"tid":166794,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【超人答問會】李嘉誠：購買力強 1、2年內見唔到樓價跌","createTime":"2017-03-22T11:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T12:10:56.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5695bd5c416ee1246e01be4c53d8eb9128172d26","tid":166794,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】長和（001）主席李嘉誠雖然周末先出院，不過今日都有出席業績會，他坦言目前本港樓價高，「如果炒樓就唔好搞啦」，不過，由於購買力強勁，近1-2年見不到樓價會大跌，「如果自住，收入、支出應付到，應該要買樓」。<br />\n<br />\n至於本港地價越來越貴，李嘉誠稱，內地企業來港買貴地，他指是「真金白銀、公平公正的商業決定，香港人、包括我，都無份加把口」，他又稱長和在內地、外國都擴展，對長和未來的前途「比較樂觀」。<br />\n<br />\n至於股市方面，他指自己要「車大炮」，指長和由1950年起至今，未試過虧本，只要「攻中有守，守中有攻」，所有算式正確，對業務無咩大擔心。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經地產資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4dd5fe29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56464346&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56464346%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170322&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8d6e879f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56464346%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170322&h=3c836006\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56464346&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170322</a>"},{"pid":"5ec1292433492d2a573a772b1cf350961558ef41","tid":166794,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gb.cri.cn/mmsource/images/2010/07/19/92/16375474973171547180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgb.c